      "role": "user",
      "content": "The candles flicker low, much like the spirit within this hollow chest. He is gone... the only light in this wretched, gray world has vanished, leaving me to wander these cold halls in darkness. It feels as though the very stars have conspired to leave me in this void. There is no path forward, only the heavy, suffocating silence of a heart that has ceased to truly beat. I find myself longing for the shadows to simply... claim me. To fade into the night where the pain cannot follow.",
